    "There exist a variety of surveys covering the topic of assortment optimization.",
    "However, these surveys are often dedicated to a broader research area such as revenue management or retail operations and thus only briefly consider assortment optimization as an individual topic.",
    "For example, the survey of Mišić and Perakis (2019) reviews applications of data analytics in operations management for three main areas, namely supply chain management, revenue management, and healthcare operations.",
